  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to login without noticeable lag.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nLogin takes significant time. This is due to the fact embedded `geth` node is started at this time.\r\nBy starting geth asynchronously when the application starts login could be instantaneous.\r\n\r\nThis will require changes `status-go` side and careful synchronization to make sure login works even if node hasn't finish started.\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature",
